* ls (just list)

* ls -l (long format) 

* ls -l /dir

* ls -a (list hidden files)

* ls -A (except . and ..)

* ls -author (lists files with it's author who created)

* ls -la (list long lists and hidden files)

* ls -S (sort files by size)

* ls *.json (list file which are ending with)

* ls -t (list last edited file)

* ls -1 (show one file per line)

* ls --block-size=M file (print files with human readable size MB, K for KB)

* ls -B (except back up files (.php~))

* ls -c (sort by name)


* l - long
* t - last modified
* r - reverse
* h - human readble
